      <event start="T151-256" end="T153-440">Ono drugo pa si ... si imel, ki si bi() ... </event>
      <event start="T154-966" end="T59">Ker si bil črn, črnec, ker si bil črn, </event>
      <event start="T59" end="T60">ne. </event>
      <event start="T60" end="T61">Ono je bilo črno, </event>
      <event start="T61" end="T62">ne, </event>
      <event start="T62" end="T160-388">po blatu tam pa les, gor, dol. </event>
      <event start="T167-021" end="T167-656">Ma ne, </event>
      <event start="T167-656" end="T170-549">ma ono za ono eee pri nas ni bilo problem, </event>
      <event start="T170-549" end="T66">k smo imeli tudi ... tudi kravo. </event>
      <event start="T66" end="T174-188">O() o() oča je molzel </event>
      <event start="T174-188" end="T68">in mi smo imeli vsak svoj lončič </event>
      <event start="T68" end="T178-336">inu pili direktno iz ko so molzli. </event>
      <event start="T179-588" end="T181-994">Kakor je molzel, tako smo pili. </event>
      <event start="T184-005" end="T69">Tako, </event>
      <event start="T69" end="T185-004">ja. </event>
      <event start="T187-856" end="T76">Ne. </event>
      <event start="T76" end="T193-940">Ma ne, maneš(), manej() ... manej() ... ma() ... </event>
      <event start="T193-940" end="T77">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T77" end="T198-607">mineštra, mineštra, mineštra in tabot, ki (), tabot je bil, </event>
