      <event start="T325-743" end="T111">Eee eee eee, eee </event>
      <event start="T111" end="T112">normalno, da ste prodali. </event>
      <event start="T112" end="T333-839">Saj mi, mi smo, mi smo tudi takrat, ki je moj oče z vozom in osla. </event>
      <event start="T334-968" end="T336-239">Voza in osla. </event>
      <event start="T336-239" end="T337-453">Samo še osel je bil </event>
      <event start="T337-453" end="T113">mmm ... </event>
      <event start="T113" end="T339-590">slep. </event>
      <event start="T339-590" end="T341-348">Smo imeli anka mi voz. </event>
      <event start="T341-348" end="T342-695">Ku ... </event>
      <event start="T343-583" end="T346-084">Si nakrgal na voz polno robe, </event>
