      <event start="T348-047" end="T349-694">je šlo za se zmotat. </event>
      <event start="T349-694" end="T351-611">Ku je bil prazen, ni hotel iti naprej. </event>
      <event start="T354-221" end="T395">Inu potem, ki je tu() ki smo imeli za pobirati grozdje in to, </event>
      <event start="T395" end="T116">smo imeli one brente, </event>
      <event start="T116" end="T117">ne, </event>
